    "description": "<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1645656213\" /></span><br><br><strong>Click the banner below to join our Discord!</strong><br><br><strong>This camping has seen better days, and now it’s up to you to make it a fantastic holiday spot once again. Camping Builder is a next-gen simulator with polished mechanics, an environment full of life, and an engaging story.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/CB_Steam_Opis_Build_it.png?t=1645656213\" /></span><br>You can gather materials and use them to rebuild the bungalows, then decorate them to your liking and wait for the guests to arrive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/GIF_Steam_Domek.gif?t=1645656213\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/CB_Steam_Opis_Keep_it.png?t=1645656213\" /></span><br>Pick up the trash and throw it away into the dedicated containers. You can also decide just to burn it or dump it into the ocean, risking the island’s wrath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/GIF_Steam_Sprzatanie.gif?t=1645656213\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/CB_Steam_Opis_Reap_what.png?t=1645656213\" /></span><br>You can cut down trees, but make sure to plant new ones! The Camping Builder is all about balance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/GIF_Steam_Sadzenie.gif?t=1645656213\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/CB_Steam_Opis_Island_full.png?t=1645656213\" /></span><br>Find out more about this beautiful place, meet its inhabitants and discover its mysteries. Fall in love with the world and the story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873850/extras/GIF_Steam_Kapibara.gif?t=1645656213\" /></span>",
